```plantuml
@startuml jquku_Matrix-Chatbot

actor User
participant "Matrix Homeserver" as Matrix
participant "Chatbot Core" as Core
participant "NLP Module" as NLP
participant "Message Evaluation" as Eval
participant "Database Service" as DB
participant "Response Management" as Response

User -> Matrix: Send message
Matrix -> Core: Receive message
Core -> NLP: Process message
NLP -> Core: Return processed message
Core -> Eval: Evaluate intent and domain
Eval -> DB: Query knowledge base
DB -> Eval: Return knowledge data
Eval -> Response: Generate response
Response -> Core: Return final response
Core -> Matrix: Send response
Matrix -> User: Deliver response

@enduml
```